text: Ivaylo Banchev (born 26 June 1971) is a Bulgarian rower. He competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Bulgaria Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Ruse, Bulgaria
